# Rust
/target
**/*.rs.bk

# Local-dev override: point edgecommons at the sibling libs/rust instead of the pinned git rev.
# Gitignored so CI uses the git rev; see the org CLAUDE.md "Local-dev notes".
/.cargo/config.toml

# Cargo.lock excluded until the edgecommons pin is bumped from the current pre-UNS placeholder rev to
# the published UNS-core rev on main and regenerated (the local build's lock records the `.cargo`
# `paths` override's resolution against the sibling checkout — a fresh clone/CI has no sibling, and a
# pure git-rev build of this placeholder rev does not compile anyway — see Cargo.toml's "UNS MIGRATION
# NOTE"). Re-commit the lock at release once the pin is bumped (mirrors telemetry-processor's UNS-core
# migration).
/Cargo.lock

# Greengrass build output
/greengrass-build
/zip-build

# Local runtime data (durable state, vault, spool/archive scratch)
/data
*.redb
vault.json
# Durable SQLite state written to the process CWD when run locally (+ WAL/SHM sidecars)
file-replicator-state.db*
# Local run logs (e.g. the metricEmission log sink's default output)
/logs/

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
